P.S. 
10:30 P.M. same day! 
Am through here. Swede audience, or at least very largely swede. They fell for it as usual, & called me from behind the curtain when I had really quit. They are not so quoteably civilized here as in Moorehead - Fargo, but they are quite all right. 
Hiddy, I've just read yoiur lette rover two glasses of beer after the show. It's a great letter, Old Kid! I needn't tell you how dear you are to me & how highly I appraise you. 

