I went into that place in Minneapolis & saw the <unclear/> with holster that was advertised. It is practically new - no sign of wear anywhere inside or outside. I wanted it a lot, but of course it would be foolish to buy it. 
The weather has been five up here - even at Moorhead what is as far worth as Duluth. I arrived for the January thaw. They have had 30 below at Moorhead 25 at Minneapolis
Endless love, Hiddy, 
Dad,
Comradely greetings to Elanita! 
