I am really happy about much, and you are a large part of the muchness! 
Had an ambrosial evening with Dr. Richard Scammon, Dean of Medical Sciences at U. of Minnesota. he is a very distinguished man. You know, he is my old "Dick"- one of my best boyhood chums, We were inseparable as she ages of 9 & 10. We got together in five shops. He & his son & their University crowd are flaming Reds. The song is leader of the Farmen Labor Party in Minnesota, & he is only 18! the kid is 5ft. 5 1/2 in tall & weighs 260 lbs, also, he has a brain big enough for a such a body. 
I feel he will get killed early in teh inevitable row. But he will be heard from How they, & another Prof., did endorse my prophetic guesses. 
